data.description: WOW! Just look at this Charmer! Large covered front porch with a swing! Walking distance to historical downtown Plattsmouth. Gorgeous original wood work throughout! Exterior has been professionally re-stuccoed & painted. Roof 2013, HVAC 2018, newer windows upstairs. 4" downspouts & gutters with leaf guards. Updated plumbing & electrical. 1 Bed/Office on the main level & 3 good size bedrooms on 2nd level. Updated bathrooms and new flooring in kitchen! Large dining room and living room. Galley kitchen with original cabinetry. Iron fenced in front yard! AMA
